      en:{name:"Montevideo Metropolitan Cathedral",type:"Metropolitan cathedral",city:"Montevideo",province:"Montevideo",description:"The mother church of Montevideo, dedicated to the Immaculate Conception and the city's patron saints Philip and James.",history:"The cathedral stands in the historic heart of Montevideo and preserves the Catholic memory of Uruguay's capital. Its sober neoclassical presence makes it a natural starting point for pilgrims in the country.",prayer:"Immaculate Mary, Saints Philip and James, pray for Montevideo and make my faith steady, humble and apostolic. Amen.",feast:"December 8 (Immaculate Conception)"},
      es:{name:"Catedral Metropolitana de Montevideo",type:"Catedral metropolitana",city:"Montevideo",province:"Montevideo",description:"La iglesia madre de Montevideo, dedicada a la Inmaculada Concepci\u00f3n y a los patronos de la ciudad, san Felipe y Santiago.",history:"La catedral se alza en el coraz\u00f3n hist\u00f3rico de Montevideo y conserva la memoria cat\u00f3lica de la capital uruguaya. Su presencia neocl\u00e1sica sobria la convierte en un punto natural de partida para peregrinos en el pa\u00eds.",prayer:"Mar\u00eda Inmaculada, santos Felipe y Santiago, rogad por Montevideo y haced mi fe firme, humilde y apost\u00f3lica. Am\u00e9n.",feast:"8 de diciembre (Inmaculada Concepci\u00f3n)"},
      fr:{name:"Cath\u00e9drale m\u00e9tropolitaine de Montevideo",type:"Cath\u00e9drale m\u00e9tropolitaine",city:"Montevideo",province:"Montevideo",description:"L'\u00e9glise m\u00e8re de Montevideo, d\u00e9di\u00e9e \u00e0 l'Immacul\u00e9e Conception et aux saints patrons de la ville, Philippe et Jacques.",history:"La cath\u00e9drale se dresse au coeur historique de Montevideo et garde la m\u00e9moire catholique de la capitale uruguayenne. Sa sobre pr\u00e9sence n\u00e9oclassique en fait un point de d\u00e9part naturel pour les p\u00e8lerins du pays.",prayer:"Marie Immacul\u00e9e, saints Philippe et Jacques, priez pour Montevideo et rendez ma foi ferme, humble et apostolique. Amen.",feast:"8 d\u00e9cembre (Immacul\u00e9e Conception)"},
      it:{name:"Cattedrale metropolitana di Montevideo",type:"Cattedrale metropolitana",city:"Montevideo",province:"Montevideo",description:"La chiesa madre di Montevideo, dedicata all'Immacolata Concezione e ai patroni della citt\u00e0, santi Filippo e Giacomo.",history:"La cattedrale sorge nel cuore storico di Montevideo e custodisce la memoria cattolica della capitale uruguaiana. La sua sobria presenza neoclassica la rende un punto naturale di partenza per i pellegrini nel paese.",prayer:"Maria Immacolata, santi Filippo e Giacomo, pregate per Montevideo e rendete la mia fede salda, umile e apostolica. Amen.",feast:"8 dicembre (Immacolata Concezione)"},
      pt:{name:"Catedral Metropolitana de Montevid\u00e9u",type:"Catedral metropolitana",city:"Montevid\u00e9u",province:"Montevid\u00e9u",description:"A igreja-m\u00e3e de Montevid\u00e9u, dedicada \u00e0 Imaculada Concei\u00e7\u00e3o e aos padroeiros da cidade, S\u00e3o Filipe e S\u00e3o Tiago.",history:"A catedral ergue-se no cora\u00e7\u00e3o hist\u00f3rico de Montevid\u00e9u e guarda a mem\u00f3ria cat\u00f3lica da capital uruguaia. A sua presen\u00e7a neocl\u00e1ssica s\u00f3bria torna-a ponto natural de partida para peregrinos no pa\u00eds.",prayer:"Maria Imaculada, S\u00e3o Filipe e S\u00e3o Tiago, rogai por Montevid\u00e9u e tornai a minha f\u00e9 firme, humilde e apost\u00f3lica. \u00c1men.",feast:"8 de dezembro (Imaculada Concei\u00e7\u00e3o)"}
